columns.name: arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) specifying the vpc.

columns.name: cidr_block
columns.description: The primary IPv4 CIDR block for the VPC.

columns.name: state
columns.description: Contains the current state of the VPC.

columns.name: is_default
columns.description: Indicates whether the VPC is the default VPC.

columns.name: dhcp_options_id
columns.description: Contains the ID of the set of DHCP options, associated with the VPC.

columns.name: instance_tenancy
columns.description: The allowed tenancy of instances launched into the VPC.

columns.name: owner_id
columns.description: Contains ID of the AWS account that owns the VPC.

columns.name: cidr_block_association_set
columns.description: Information about the IPv4 CIDR blocks associated with the VPC.

columns.name: ipv6_cidr_block_association_set
columns.description: Information about the IPv6 CIDR blocks associated with the VPC.

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: A list of tags that are attached with the VPC.
